CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1954, pg. 17, reads: "City Council - Pittsburgh's governing body during the next two years will include, front row, left to right, Councilman A. L. Wolk, John F. Couahan, Emanual [Emmanuel] F. Schifano, President Thomas J. Gallagher, Paul F. Jones and Patrick T. Fagan. Behind them are Fredrick G. Weir, Charles Dinan and Bennett Rodgers."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of Pittsburgh City Council members, from left: A. L. Wolk, Fredrick G. Weir, John F. Couahan, Charles Dinan, Emanuel F. Schifano, President Thomas J. Gallagher, Bennett Rodgers, Paul F. Jones, and Patrick T. Fagan, gathered in office with scroll patterned carpet, and portrait and cartoon framed on wall
